{"id":232873864,"title":"#問 決勝時刻 系列WWII 、現代戰爭","content":"想問一下，我是一個喜歡玩槍戰的玩家，但並不喜歡線上對戰，只喜歡玩故事模式。\n\n我第一款決勝時刻遊戲是 WWII PS4 ，一買覺得驚訝，感覺錢花對了，那個畫質，那個搖桿震動，阿斯～～\n\n但玩不久才發現，故事的關卡似乎只有不到10關（全部都困難模式破完了），讓我覺得不是很值，有試著玩過線上對戰，但就不是我喜歡的感覺。\n\n最近打算過年買 現代戰爭 ，看到那個預告有點受不了，但怕他的關卡跟二戰一樣少，就讓我不是很想買了，（二戰還出一堆dlc 我暈）\n\n想問有買現代戰爭的，想請問關卡多嗎？ 耐玩嗎？\n適合我這個不玩線上多人的玩家嗎？\n\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/6470aa2d-32bc-4916-adb2-7a764a3d7bbe/full.jpeg","excerpt":"想問一下，我是一個喜歡玩槍戰的玩家，但並不喜歡線上對戰，只喜歡玩故事模式。我第一款決勝時刻遊戲是 WWII PS4 ，一買覺得驚訝，感覺錢花對了，那個畫質，那個搖桿震動，阿斯～～但玩不久才發現，故事的","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"72f262c4-75aa-4d75-ab0e-cd7bd09e69b5","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-11T17:00:15.342Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-11T17:01:48.407Z","commentCount":6,"likeCount":0,"tags":[],"topics":["遊戲","PS4"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"遊戲","forumAlias":"game","school":"中國文化大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/6470aa2d-32bc-4916-adb2-7a764a3d7bbe/full.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"957f466b-22c5-4968-99d5-f7b7c15dda5b","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/6470aa2d-32bc-4916-adb2-7a764a3d7bbe/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/6470aa2d-32bc-4916-adb2-7a764a3d7bbe/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/6470aa2d-32bc-4916-adb2-7a764a3d7bbe/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-11T17:00:15.342Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-11T17:01:48.407Z","width":640,"height":240},{"id":"957f466b-22c5-4968-99d5-f7b7c15dda5b","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/6470aa2d-32bc-4916-adb2-7a764a3d7bbe/full.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx.dcard.tw/v1/images/6470aa2d-32bc-